title: DDFP 466: Remaining Free Agents, 2016 Ravens & 'Dead or Alive'
itunes:title: DDFP 466: Remaining Free Agents, 2016 Ravens & 'Dead or Alive'
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Michael Fabiano to discuss the top remaining free agents, the best Fantasy players going into 2016 and preview the 2016 Ravens. The guys also determine how the 1985 Bears would fare against today's quarterbacks. Also, Shek goes on a "Walk & Talk with A.J. Hawk." Plus, the guys compete in another surprise game show and wrap with a chat about their “Game of Thrones” Fantasy rankings.
